<br>
Go to Lenka Stoutheart, a female barb who shares a hut with an ogre.  Hail her, then tell her &quot;I want to see something interesting.&quot;  This spawns Sir Hobble..<br>
<br>
Find Sir Hobble and hail him.  This spawns Squire Fuzzmin.  <br>
<br>
